title: Arabian Journal of Chemistry (2008-2015)
description:
ISSN: 1878-5352

The Arabian Journal of Chemistry is an English language, peer-reviewed publication in the area of chemistry. The Arabian Journal of Chemistry publishes original papers, reviews and short reports on, but not limited to: inorganic, physical, organic, analytical and biochemistry.
The Arabian Journal of Chemistry is issued by the Arab Union of Chemists and is published by King Saud University together with the Saudi Chemical Society in collaboration with Elsevier and is edited by an international group of eminent researchers
